item.title: SoftLayer_Product_Item_Bundles
item.description: SoftLayer_Product_Item_Bundles Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Product_Item_Bundles contains item to price cross references Relates a category, price and item to a bundle. Match bundle ids to see all items and prices in a particular bundle. Local bundleItemId Identifier for bundle. Type: integer id Identifier for record. Type: integer itemPriceId Identifier for price. Type: integer Relational bundleItem Item in bundle.
